Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.55,0:00:25.17,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,So we finally meet,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.95,0:00:26.92,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,DIO!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.93,0:00:34.37,JoJo-main,dio,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations, Polnareff. \NYou've avenged your sister,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.37,0:00:38.75,JoJo-main,dio,0000,0000,0000,,and managed to travel from \Nthe Far East to make it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.59,0:00:44.60,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to give me a prize for that, \Nhow about you give me your life?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.71,0:00:51.82,JoJo-main,dio,0000,0000,0000,,I shall give you a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.33,0:00:54.57,JoJo-main,dio,0000,0000,0000,,Go down two steps,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.88,0:00:57.16,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,and I'll let you join my side again.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.63,0:01:02.49,JoJo-main,dio,0000,0000,0000,,But if you'd rather die,\Nthen climb those stairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.39,0:01:06.78,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,When I first met you,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.78,0:01:11.78,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I succumbed from the bottom of my heart\Nto your spell of fear and immense evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.34,0:01:16.62,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,That was when I became a loser.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.09,0:01:18.80,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,It's much scarier than death,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.80,0:01:22.93,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,living with no desire but to do your bidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.79,0:01:28.15,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,But right now, I don't feel any fear at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.15,0:01:30.17,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,I feel only my will to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.60,0:01:32.35,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Since I met Mr. Joestar and the others,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.35,0:01:35.50,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,this journey of 45 days \Nand the death of my friends
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.50,0:01:38.41,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,have completely blown away my fear of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.60,0:01:42.73,JoJo-main,dio,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.73,0:01:45.45,JoJo-main,dio,0000,0000,0000,,Then climb those stairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.18,0:01:53.74,JoJo-main,dio,0000,0000,0000,,I see, Polnareff.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.55,0:02:00.06,JoJo-main,dio,0000,0000,0000,,You've gone down the stairs,\Nwhich means you wish to join me, DIO.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.63,0:02:12.65,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?! I know I just took a step up...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.89,0:02:16.24,JoJo-main,dio,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter? You're losing \Nyour composure, Polnareff.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.68,0:02:21.16,JoJo-main,dio,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't one lose his \Ncomposure when he is afraid?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.38,0:02:25.94,JoJo-main,dio,0000,0000,0000,,Or is it that in your heart, \Nyou know you must climb up,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.94,0:02:28.08,JoJo-main,dio,0000,0000,0000,,but you're so terrified that your body
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.08,0:02:31.44,JoJo-main,dio,0000,0000,0000,,subconsciously did the opposite and went down?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.62,0:02:34.90,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible! I know I went up the stairs!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.16,0:02:41.93,JoJo-internal/narrator,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What did he do?! Is it his Stand?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.99,0:02:44.70,JoJo-internal/narrator,jean,0000,0000,0000,,I-It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.22,0:02:49.65,JoJo-internal/narrator,jean,0000,0000,0000,,DIO's Stand...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.97,0:02:53.57,JoJo-internal/narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,The World?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.10,0:02:57.30,JoJo-internal/narrator,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.01,0:04:25.93,JoJo-MainTitle,title,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(208,2515)}JoJo's {\c&H2E0FB2&}Bizarre Adventure
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.01,0:04:25.93,JoJo-MainTitle2,title,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(208,2515)}Stardust Crusaders
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.22,0:04:34.64,JoJo-EpTitle,epi,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(458,632)}Episode 45  DIO's World, Part 1
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.86,0:04:35.50,JoJo-top,dio,0000,0000,0000,,Polnareff, have you ever considered \Nwhy humans wish to live?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.82,0:04:38.75,JoJo-top,dio,0000,0000,0000,,Humans live hoping to conquer \Ntheir anxieties and fears,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.56,0:04:42.41,JoJo-Location,blahlala,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(459,459)\b0\fs18}This story is fiction. The characters, groups, places, laws, and names \Nused in this program have no connection to any existing in real life.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.75,0:04:40.96,JoJo-top,,0000,0000,0000,,and attain peace of mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.53,0:04:43.44,JoJo-top,dio,0000,0000,0000,,Seeking fame,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.09,0:04:45.80,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,controlling others,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.80,0:04:49.01,JoJo-main,dio,0000,0000,0000,,and acquiring wealth are all\Ndone to achieve peace of mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.01,0:04:53.43,JoJo-main,dio,0000,0000,0000,,Marriage and friendship are also pursued\Nas means of attaining peace of mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.88,0:04:55.89,JoJo-main,dio,0000,0000,0000,,When humans say they wish to help others,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.89,0:04:58.06,JoJo-main,dio,0000,0000,0000,,or that a thing is done for love or justice...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.35,0:05:00.84,JoJo-main,dio,0000,0000,0000,,It's all merely to give themselves peace of mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.27,0:05:04.67,JoJo-main,dio,0000,0000,0000,,To achieve peace of mind \Nis the goal of all mankind.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.73,0:05:10.70,JoJo-main,dio,0000,0000,0000,,Now, given that, what anxiety could \Nyou possibly feel toward serving me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.97,0:05:14.10,JoJo-main,dio,0000,0000,0000,,Any other peace of mind \Nwill come easily if you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.00,0:05:20.47,JoJo-main,dio,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't challenging me, even knowing \Nthat it may spell your death,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.47,0:05:22.17,JoJo-main,dio,0000,0000,0000,,bring you anxiety?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.64,0:05:26.80,JoJo-internal/narrator,jean,0000,0000,0000,,I-It can't be! Am I subconsciously \Nsubmitting to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.15,0:05:29.65,JoJo-main,dio,0000,0000,0000,,You are a very capable Stand user.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.09,0:05:31.37,JoJo-main,dio,0000,0000,0000,,It's a waste to kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.80,0:05:33.94,JoJo-main,dio,0000,0000,0000,,Why not cut ties with Joestar and the others,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.94,0:05:36.35,JoJo-main,dio,0000,0000,0000,,and serve me for eternity?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.74,0:05:39.95,JoJo-main,dio,0000,0000,0000,,I can promise you peace of mind for eternity.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.95,0:05:41.44,JoJo-internal/narrator,jean,0000,0000,0000,,I can't go on like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.03,0:05:45.03,JoJo-internal/narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,Avdol, Iggy... Give me courage!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.18,0:05:47.77,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You talk too much, DIO!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.77,0:05:49.57,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,I've already died once.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.19,0:05:55.33,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,I won't die again until I figure out \Nthe identity of your Stand!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.97,0:05:59.38,JoJo-main,dio,0000,0000,0000,,You leave me no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.26,0:06:07.77,JoJo-main,dio,0000,0000,0000,,Then you'll just have to die, Polnareff!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.14,0:06:11.68,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,So that's The World? Bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.00,0:06:15.14,JoJo-main,dio,0000,0000,0000,,Useless! Useless! Useless! Useless!\NUseless! Useless! Useless! Useless! Useless!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.91,0:06:27.79,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,M-Mr. Joestar!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.41,0:06:31.28,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, Polnareff.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.69,0:06:35.83,JoJo-main,all,0000,0000,0000,,DIO!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.83,0:06:37.83,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,That was DIO, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.83,0:06:39.18,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,We're going after him!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.18,0:06:41.51,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Before you go after him, let me say this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.51,0:06:45.75,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,I just experienced his Stand, just for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.12,0:06:50.53,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, it wasn't so much an experience... \NIt was completely beyond my understanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.05,0:06:54.01,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'll tell you exactly what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.41,0:06:58.19,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I was climbing the stairs\Ntoward him, but before I knew it,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.19,0:06:59.89,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I was actually going down!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.48,0:07:03.64,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sure you guys don't \Nunderstand what I'm saying,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.97,0:07:06.32,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,and I don't know what he did, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.99,0:07:09.30,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I was going insane.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.30,0:07:14.83,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't anything simple, \Nlike hypnosis or super speed...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.28,0:07:18.70,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,I experienced something much more terrifying.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.81,0:07:24.39,JoJo-main,jojo,0000,0000,0000,,Where are Avdol and Iggy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.15,0:07:30.91,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Th-They didn't make it...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.94,0:07:34.66,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,They died saving me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.21,0:07:42.50,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.11,0:07:50.29,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Joestar, the sun is setting.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.73,0:07:52.07,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,We must hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.13,0:07:54.53,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.67,0:07:59.43,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Nukesaku. What's above this floor?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.43,0:08:01.04,JoJo-main,nuke,0000,0000,0000,,A-A tower.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.04,0:08:03.40,JoJo-main,nuke,0000,0000,0000,,There is a single room at the very top.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.40,0:08:05.46,JoJo-main,nuke,0000,0000,0000,,Lord DIO stays there during the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.46,0:08:07.66,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,Do any other staircases lead up to that tower?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.66,0:08:10.49,JoJo-main,nuke,0000,0000,0000,,N-No. These stairs are the only way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.49,0:08:12.19,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,All right. Lead the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.50,0:08:33.60,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,So that's him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.91,0:08:36.68,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,The man we're about to face
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.03,0:08:40.58,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,is one I've never met, \Nyet one I've known for so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.38,0:08:44.40,JoJo-internal/narrator,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I have always known him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.71,0:08:47.97,JoJo-internal/narrator,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,I've known him since the day I was born.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.58,0:08:50.27,JoJo-internal/narrator,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,The same goes for Jotaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.17,0:08:53.62,JoJo-internal/narrator,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,He's not someone we have fond memories of.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.62,0:08:55.65,JoJo-internal/narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,Our Joestar blood always knew that
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.65,0:08:59.32,JoJo-internal/narrator,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,he was someone we would encounter \None day, someone we must defeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.90,0:09:01.30,JoJo-internal/narrator,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,I have no regrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.63,0:09:05.29,JoJo-internal/narrator,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,The journey we've made,\Nthe events about to transpire...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.64,0:09:07.33,JoJo-internal/narrator,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,I regret none of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.68,0:09:13.73,JoJo-internal/narrator,jean,0000,0000,0000,,What I'm feeling right now \Ntells me the side I'm on is white.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.48,0:09:15.52,JoJo-internal/narrator,jean,0000,0000,0000,,DIO's side is black.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.89,0:09:17.66,JoJo-internal/narrator,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Joestar and the others, too, are white.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.24,0:09:21.19,JoJo-internal/narrator,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Despite my injuries, I can \Nfeel my courage growing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.87,0:09:25.17,JoJo-internal/narrator,jean,0000,0000,0000,,I am on the white side,\Nthe side of righteousness!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.20,0:09:29.21,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Once he steps out of the coffin, we'll attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.21,0:09:30.70,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,But be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.70,0:09:33.10,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no guarantee that he's in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.15,0:09:37.63,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Nukesaku, open the lid.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.44,0:09:43.89,JoJo-main,nuke,0000,0000,0000,,L-Lord DIO, I promise, I did not betray you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.29,0:09:50.28,JoJo-main,nuke,0000,0000,0000,,It's because I truly believe in \Nyour power that I led them here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.28,0:09:55.84,JoJo-main,nuke,0000,0000,0000,,As certain as when you piss in a \Nstrong wind, it'll get on your pants!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.84,0:09:58.11,JoJo-main,nuke,0000,0000,0000,,Please understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.11,0:10:01.59,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up and open it already!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.73,0:10:07.29,JoJo-main,nuke,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure you kill these bastards,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.33,0:10:10.17,JoJo-main,nuke,0000,0000,0000,,Lord DIO!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.19,0:10:12.53,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,He's going to come flying out!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.43,0:10:19.18,JoJo-main,nuke,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.55,0:10:20.51,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.49,0:10:27.27,JoJo-main,nuke,0000,0000,0000,,I-I was the one inside?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.27,0:10:29.87,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,But I was the one that opened the lid!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.19,0:10:30.81,JoJo-overlap,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?! How?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.81,0:10:33.11,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,I never took my eyes off him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.11,0:10:35.71,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Did any of you see the \Nmoment Nukesaku entered...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.71,0:10:38.70,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,No, was put into the coffin?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.70,0:10:41.19,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,N-No... I was watching the whole time,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.19,0:10:43.95,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,but when I realized it, he was already inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.95,0:10:49.00,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,It's as Polnareff said!\NThis is not merely a trick or super speed!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.41,0:10:50.37,JoJo-main,jojo,0000,0000,0000,,We're in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.37,0:10:52.27,JoJo-main,jojo,0000,0000,0000,,Something here is truly dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.13,0:10:57.46,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.46,0:11:00.01,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,D-Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.01,0:11:02.67,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, Polnareff?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.93,0:11:07.68,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.33,0:11:12.88,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.34,0:11:15.96,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't actually see it, but it felt much
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.96,0:11:19.04,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,more powerful than any Stand \Nwe've encountered so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.04,0:11:23.74,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,It was like knowing a bulldozer is present\Nfrom the sound of its engine alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.01,0:11:27.52,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,I felt it, too. It was incredible murderous intent!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.52,0:11:30.52,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,It felt like someone stuck an icicle up my ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.52,0:11:34.50,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,If we had stayed in there,\Nwe would've been killed, one by one!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.37,0:11:51.89,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad... This is extremely bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.89,0:11:54.15,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,The sun's almost out of sight!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.52,0:11:56.76,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,His time has come.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.15,0:12:01.29,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me that we're
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.29,0:12:04.28,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,going to be helpless until sunrise tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.56,0:12:06.48,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,I'll telling you now, Mr. Joestar!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.48,0:12:10.04,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way I'm going to run away now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.45,0:12:13.46,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,I agree with Polnareff.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.09,0:12:21.81,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,I feel the same way, \Nbut the situation has changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.15,0:12:25.17,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,We've encountered his Stand, The World,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.17,0:12:27.69,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,but we have no idea what it does.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.69,0:12:30.38,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,When climbing a mountain,\Nif you don't know the route,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.38,0:12:32.75,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,or where the summit is,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.75,0:12:35.73,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,you are guaranteed to get lost. Guaranteed!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.08,0:12:40.71,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,It's as inevitable as belching \Nafter you drink a cola.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.03,0:12:44.85,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,We know DIO will come after us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.85,0:12:47.16,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll try to finish us before sunrise.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.65,0:12:50.42,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,In that time, we'll have\Nthe opportunity to figure out
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.42,0:12:51.83,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,his Stand's true ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.62,0:12:54.58,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,We have to wait for that chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.58,0:12:57.23,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,No! I can't run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.23,0:12:59.82,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Avdol and Iggy died for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.25,0:13:04.04,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do underhanded things, \Nand even go to Hell itself,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.04,0:13:07.43,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,but I will not run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.43,0:13:09.62,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Polnareff!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.62,0:13:11.77,JoJo-main,jojo,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use trying to stop him, old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.00,0:13:14.89,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,Jotaro, tell us what you think we should do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.56,0:13:20.27,JoJo-main,jojo,0000,0000,0000,,Polnareff is fighting him as he pursues him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.77,0:13:23.28,JoJo-main,jojo,0000,0000,0000,,We'll fight him as we retreat.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.85,0:13:24.90,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,That means
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.90,0:13:27.28,JoJo-main,jojo,0000,0000,0000,,we'll be in position for a pincer attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.53,0:13:32.66,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.66,0:13:35.21,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,I want to buy that truck. Sell it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.70,0:13:38.97,JoJo-main,driver,0000,0000,0000,,What'd you say? I need this to do my job!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.97,0:13:40.03,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.77,0:13:45.34,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,I'm flooring it, Kakyoin!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.87,0:14:04.72,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,There you are, DIO!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.72,0:14:08.28,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Run away until sunrise? Like hell I can do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.54,0:14:10.31,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,I'll finish you myself if I must!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.31,0:14:13.60,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,If I don't know what your Stand is, \Nthen even without that knowledge,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.60,0:14:16.00,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,there are still plenty of ways to beat you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.96,0:14:18.14,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,I'll assassinate you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.14,0:14:19.50,JoJo-main,jojo,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do anything rash, Polnareff!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.92,0:14:25.14,JoJo-main,jojo,0000,0000,0000,,I told them to leave someone \Nas stubborn as you alone,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.70,0:14:29.26,JoJo-main,jojo,0000,0000,0000,,but the old man and Kakyoin \Ninsisted that I stay with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.26,0:14:30.47,JoJo-main,jojo,0000,0000,0000,,So here I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.98,0:14:32.27,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Jotaro...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.88,0:14:35.41,JoJo-main,jojo,0000,0000,0000,,Good grief.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.27,0:14:42.98,JoJo-Eyecatch3,signtop,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(818,1)}The World
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.98,0:14:57.25,JoJo-main,dio,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, the automobile...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.58,0:14:59.58,JoJo-main,dio,0000,0000,0000,,Its power and speed are impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.30,0:15:03.75,JoJo-main,dio,0000,0000,0000,,In my day, we had only horse-drawn carriages.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.48,0:15:06.92,JoJo-main,guy,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What do you think you're touching?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.92,0:15:10.14,JoJo-main,body,0000,0000,0000,,This car belongs to Senator Phillips!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.14,0:15:12.30,JoJo-main,body,0000,0000,0000,,Do you wanna puke from your eyes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.88,0:15:27.77,JoJo-main,wil,0000,0000,0000,,My, my... Young folks are \Nso hot-blooded these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.16,0:15:32.57,JoJo-main,wil,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.81,0:15:36.66,JoJo-main,dio,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up and get in the front seat. \NYou're going to drive.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.66,0:15:39.13,JoJo-main,wil,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Who the hell are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.13,0:15:42.92,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think you're going \Nto get away with this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.92,0:15:45.09,JoJo-internal/narrator,wil,0000,0000,0000,,No, of course he won't!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.09,0:15:48.13,JoJo-internal/narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,No one could get away with doing this to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.13,0:15:50.60,JoJo-internal/narrator,wil,0000,0000,0000,,I graduated high school and \Ncollege at the top of my class!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.60,0:15:53.18,JoJo-internal/narrator,wil,0000,0000,0000,,I was captain of my college wrestling team!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.18,0:15:56.30,JoJo-internal/narrator,wil,0000,0000,0000,,Even after I graduated, \NI was respected and revered.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.30,0:15:57.72,JoJo-internal/narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how I became a politician!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.72,0:15:59.88,JoJo-internal/narrator,wil,0000,0000,0000,,I have a villa on a thousand acres in Hawaii!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.88,0:16:02.94,JoJo-internal/narrator,wil,0000,0000,0000,,I married a beautiful model \Nwho's 25 years younger than me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.94,0:16:05.42,JoJo-internal/narrator,wil,0000,0000,0000,,I pay 50 times more in taxes\Nthan ordinary people!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.72,0:16:07.90,JoJo-internal/narrator,wil,0000,0000,0000,,I've defeated every enemy that I've faced.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.90,0:16:13.41,JoJo-internal/narrator,wil,0000,0000,0000,,I'll eventually become president. \NI am Senator Phillips!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.71,0:16:16.12,JoJo-main,wil,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up, young buck!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.12,0:16:17.53,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll get life in prison for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.53,0:16:19.73,JoJo-main,wil,0000,0000,0000,,You hear me? Life in prison—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.73,0:16:21.16,JoJo-main,dio,0000,0000,0000,,I'll say it once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.24,0:16:25.59,JoJo-main,dio,0000,0000,0000,,Drive.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.89,0:16:30.76,JoJo-internal/narrator,wil,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Who the hell is he? He's going to kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.76,0:16:32.33,JoJo-internal/narrator,wil,0000,0000,0000,,If I don't escape, he'll kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.33,0:16:34.89,JoJo-internal/narrator,wil,0000,0000,0000,,If I don't escape, he {\i0}will{\i1} kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.28,0:16:37.57,JoJo-main,wil,0000,0000,0000,,Help... me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.52,0:16:42.25,JoJo-main,wil,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.47,0:16:46.95,JoJo-main,wil,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.95,0:16:52.17,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I jumped outside, \Nso wh-why... why... am I inside...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.17,0:16:53.63,JoJo-main,wil,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.98,0:16:57.28,JoJo-main,dio,0000,0000,0000,,Floor it until you catch up to that truck.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.56,0:17:00.04,JoJo-main,dio,0000,0000,0000,,If you fail to catch up to it, I'll kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.04,0:17:01.90,JoJo-main,wil,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.26,0:17:04.62,JoJo-internal/narrator,wil,0000,0000,0000,,Why inside?! Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.62,0:17:07.75,JoJo-internal/narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,I know! It's because I'm a senator!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.75,0:17:10.05,JoJo-internal/narrator,wil,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing a senator can't do!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.03,0:17:24.82,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,The black atmosphere that emanates \Nfrom him is still close...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.25,0:17:26.86,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,It's coming after us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.86,0:17:28.81,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's{\i0} coming after us!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.17,0:17:32.61,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,Can DIO tell exactly where you are, Mr. Joestar?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.01,0:17:37.94,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,No. His body is that of my \Ngrandfather, Jonathan Joestar.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.94,0:17:41.69,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,We can sense each other due to something \Nlike a strange wavelength between us,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.69,0:17:45.33,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,but we can only tell that the \Nother is close, not where he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.83,0:17:50.42,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't tell exactly where the mansion was, \Neither, even though we were nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.75,0:17:55.75,JoJo-main,jsoeph,0000,0000,0000,,All he can sense is that a Joestar is nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.75,0:17:58.56,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,He can't tell the difference\Nbetween Jotaro and myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.05,0:18:03.26,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,He shouldn't be able to realize that \NJotaro and I have split up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.15,0:18:06.81,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,That's strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.11,0:18:10.40,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,In movies, the engine always starts right up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.69,0:18:17.91,JoJo-main,wil,0000,0000,0000,,W-We're stuck in traffic.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.33,0:18:21.90,JoJo-main,wil,0000,0000,0000,,Rush hour traffic in the \Nevening is bumper to bumper.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.90,0:18:22.89,JoJo-main,dio,0000,0000,0000,,Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.37,0:18:26.29,JoJo-main,wil,0000,0000,0000,,You say that, but I can't move forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.64,0:18:29.25,JoJo-main,dio,0000,0000,0000,,The sidewalk is wide enough. Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.25,0:18:31.19,JoJo-main,wil,0000,0000,0000,,The sidewalk?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.19,0:18:33.81,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's packed with people heading home from work!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.81,0:18:35.67,JoJo-main,dio,0000,0000,0000,,That makes no difference. Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.99,0:18:37.93,JoJo-main,wil,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.21,0:18:40.12,JoJo-main,dio,0000,0000,0000,,Floor it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.12,0:18:41.72,JoJo-main,wil,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.77,0:18:52.88,JoJo-main,jojo,0000,0000,0000,,It started. Hurry up and get on, Polnareff.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.88,0:18:54.27,JoJo-main,pol,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.39,0:19:00.31,JoJo-main,wil,0000,0000,0000,,I've gone to such lengths for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.31,0:19:06.20,JoJo-main,wil,0000,0000,0000,,You'll spare my life... You'll spare\Nthis senator's life now, won't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.63,0:19:07.58,JoJo-main,dio,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.78,0:19:13.11,JoJo-internal/narrator,wil,0000,0000,0000,,I see! This is a dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.11,0:19:15.84,JoJo-internal/narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,A senator like me could never die this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.84,0:19:18.84,JoJo-internal/narrator,wil,0000,0000,0000,,It's a dream! A dream! Hooray!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.29,0:19:23.14,JoJo-main,dio,0000,0000,0000,,There he is. Get closer to them. Closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.44,0:19:26.17,JoJo-main,dio,0000,0000,0000,,If I'm not close, I cannot use The World.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.91,0:19:30.89,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,He's getting closer. It's that car! DIO's in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.00,0:19:34.22,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Kakyoin!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.70,0:19:38.99,JoJo-main,dio,0000,0000,0000,,Kakyoin's...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.99,0:19:42.36,JoJo-main,hg,0000,0000,0000,,Take this, DIO! Emerald Splash!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.33,0:20:00.93,JoJo-main,hg,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What is he?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.93,0:20:03.10,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,He didn't so much as move from his seat,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.10,0:20:05.10,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,but he managed to dodge with just one finger!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.10,0:20:06.56,JoJo-main,hg,0000,0000,0000,,How about this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.95,0:20:15.69,JoJo-main,hg,0000,0000,0000,,Even when I concentrated the Splash,\Nhe dodged. D-Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.85,0:20:19.57,JoJo-main,hg,0000,0000,0000,,When did he release his Stand?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.57,0:20:21.90,JoJo-main,hg,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible! How could I not notice?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.30,0:20:28.87,JoJo-main,dio,0000,0000,0000,,He was a bit too far away.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.39,0:20:32.16,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,He went flying out of The World's range.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.60,0:20:37.42,JoJo-main,wil,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's happening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.91,0:20:41.55,JoJo-main,dio,0000,0000,0000,,Would it benefit me in any way if I told you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.88,0:20:44.15,JoJo-main,dio,0000,0000,0000,,Keep your eyes forward and drive.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.91,0:20:52.58,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Careful, Kakyoin! You got too close to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.97,0:20:55.56,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,I-I apologize. I-I couldn't help it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.72,0:21:00.75,JoJo-internal/narrator,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,A few months ago, he said,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.75,0:21:03.98,JoJo-internal/narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,"There's no need to make\Nyourself vomit from fright."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.32,0:21:07.57,JoJo-internal/narrator,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,"Relax. Relax, Kakyoin..."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.57,0:21:11.58,JoJo-internal/narrator,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! Never again! I will never lose again!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.84,0:21:15.34,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Kakyoin, are you all right? \NDid you see The World?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.76,0:21:19.72,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... I attacked from around ten meters away.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.72,0:21:22.61,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,If I had gotten any closer, \NI would have been done for.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.07,0:21:24.84,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,It's obvious that his Stand
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.84,0:21:28.33,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,has some terrifying secret far\Nbeyond anything we can imagine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.15,0:21:31.22,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,But I've managed to figure out two things.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.61,0:21:35.92,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,First, it can't attack over distance like\NHierophant Green and Hermit Purple.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.35,0:21:38.80,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,It's a close-range power type, like Star Platinum.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.80,0:21:40.96,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,Its range is about ten meters.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.58,0:21:44.17,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,Second, it attacked with its fist.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.17,0:21:46.25,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,So it doesn't use ranged attacks, like bullets.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.17,0:21:50.89,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,If we can get within ten meters\Nof DIO without him noticing,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.89,0:21:53.16,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I think we may have a chance of defeating him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.71,0:21:55.66,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,We need to investigate carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.66,0:22:00.19,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,There's no such thing as being too \Ncautious when it comes to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.83,0:22:04.76,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,That's strange. His car stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.13,0:22:11.10,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out! Something's flying at us!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.78,0:22:17.96,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Joestar!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.50,0:22:47.46,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, Kakyoin?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.46,0:22:48.94,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,I've got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.00,0:22:54.30,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I've figured out a way to reveal \Nwhat DIO's Stand truly is.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.97,0:23:36.97,JoJo-Preview,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.54,0:23:40.19,JoJo-main,kakyoin,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder why I get goosebumps \Nwhen I think about Avdol and Iggy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.94,0:23:44.42,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps because they were the first \Nfriends I shared a common goal with.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.79,0:23:47.03,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,This journey to defeat DIO...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.78,0:23:50.03,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,Show me your Stand, DIO!
